4Geeks Academy offers a comprehensive Data Science and Machine Learning bootcamp designed for beginners. Over 16 weeks, students learn Python, SQL, Looker, and Statistics, equipping them to become proficient Data Analysts. The course includes hands-on experience with predictive modeling, algorithms, and AI project development, preparing participants for real-world challenges.

The program features three classes per week with a maximum of 12 students, ensuring personalized attention. Graduates receive a recognized certificate. The course is available in English and Spanish, with no prior experience required. For more details, please visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning). stop